reviewText: Sure, it adheres to sitcom rules, but this show gets better and better.  Simply put, it is a pleasure watching Patrick Warburton, David Spade and the lesser known Adhir Kalyan do what they do best.  And the women are (hot) a hoot, to boot!
Title: Rules of Engagement: Season 4

reviewText: This is one of my husband and mine favorite television shows. It was a great price too. . . much cheaper then I found at any local store or online.
